===Verb===
{{en-verb|nest|nests|nested|nesting}}

#{{transitive}} To [[settle]] into a home.
#:''We loved the new house and were nesting there in 2 days!''
#{{transitive}} Of animals: To [[settle]] into their nests.
#{{transitive}} To place one thing neatly inside another, and both inside yet another.
#{{intransitive}} To [[successive]]ly [[neat]]ly [[fit]] [[inside]] another.
#:''I bought a set of nesting mixing bowls for mom.''

